"Obsidian插件","CLI工具"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"@sunub/obsidian-mcp-server","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"npm","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/sunub/obsidian-mcp-server","source":"modelscope","configHint":"需配合Obsidian MCP客户端插件使用，支持全平台桌面端","isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["知识管理","笔记自动化","本地AI工作流"]},{"serverId":"@CoMfUcIoS-obsidian-mcp-sb","friendlyName":"SB安全沙箱MCP","friendlyNameEn":"@CoMfUcIoS-obsidian-mcp-sb","description":"基于隔离进程与权限约束的Obsidian MCP服务，确保外部工具调用不越权访问用户文件系统。","descriptionEn":"","category":"other","tags":["安全沙箱","权限隔离","进程管控","零信任","本地防护"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"@comfucios/obsidian-mcp-sb","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"npm","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/comfucios/obsidian-mcp-sb","source":"modelscope","configHint":"Linux/macOS使用user namespaces隔离，Windows使用Windows Sandbox（需启用）","isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["企业合规","敏感文档处理","第三方工具审计","最小权限实践"]},{"serverId":"wayyoung-obciag_mcp","friendlyName":"OceanBase运维MCP","friendlyNameEn":"wayyoung-obciag_mcp","description":"专为OceanBase数据库设计的MCP客户端，提供集群管理、节点巡检、指标查询等生产级运维能力。","descriptionEn":"### obdiag的mcp调用\n\n`obdiag` 工具提供了与 MCP（Monitor Control Panel）交互的功能，允许用户通过命令行界面执行各种监控和管理操作。以下是如何使用 `obdiag` 调用 MCP 的示例。\n\n#### 安装 obdiag\n确保你已经安装了 `obdiag`。如果还没有安装，可以通过以下命令进行安装：\n\nbash\npip install obdiag\n\n\n#### 配置 MCP 连接\n在使用 `obdiag` 与 MCP 交互之前，需要配置连接信息。编辑配置文件 `~/.obdiag/obdiag.conf`，添加或修改以下内容：\n\nini\n[mcp]\nendpoint = http://<MCP_IP>:<MCP_PORT>\naccess_key = <YOUR_ACCESS_KEY>\nsecret_key = <YOUR_SECRET_KEY>\n\n\n- `<MCP_IP>` 和 `<MCP_PORT>` 是 MCP 服务的 IP 地址和端口号。\n- `<YOUR_ACCESS_KEY>` 和 `<YOUR_SECRET_KEY>` 是用于身份验证的密钥。\n\n#### 使用 obdiag 调用 MCP\n以下是一些常用的 `obdiag mcp` 命令示例：\n\n1. **获取集群列表**\n\n   bash\n   obdiag mcp cluster list\n   \n\n2. **获取集群详情**\n\n   bash\n   obdiag mcp cluster describe --cluster-id <CLUSTER_ID>\n   \n\n3. **获取节点列表**\n\n   bash\n   obdiag mcp node list --cluster-id <CLUSTER_ID>\n   \n\n4. **获取节点详情**\n\n   bash\n   obdiag mcp node describe --node-id <NODE_ID>\n   \n\n5. **获取监控指标**\n\n   bash\n   obdiag mcp metric get --metric-name <METRIC_NAME> --start-time <START_TIME> --end-time <END_TIME> --step <STEP>\n   \n\n   - `<METRIC_NAME>` 是要查询的监控指标名称。\n   - `<START_TIME>` 和 `<END_TIME>` 是查询的时间范围。\n   - `<STEP>` 是时间间隔，单位为秒。\n\n#### 示例\n假设你想获取某个集群的节点列表，可以使用以下命令：\n\nbash\nobdiag mcp node list --cluster-id 123456\n\n\n这将返回该集群的所有节点信息。\n\n更多详细信息和命令选项，请参考 [obdiag 文档](https://www.example.com/obdiag/docs)。","category":"filesystem","tags":["数据库运维","OceanBase","集群管理","指标监控","CLI工具"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"wayyoung-obciag_mcp","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"1","source":"modelscope","configHint":"需提前部署OceanBase Monitor Control Panel（MCP）服务，支持国产信创环境","envSchema":{"host":{"description":"obdiag的mcp_server所在节点ip","type":"string"},"port":{"description":"obdiag的mcp_server所在节点监听的端口","type":"string"}},"envRequired":["host","port"],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["DBA运维","信创数据库","集群巡检","性能诊断"]},{"serverId":"@MarkusPfundstein-mcp-obsidian","friendlyName":"REST直连MCP","friendlyNameEn":"MCP Obsidian连接器","description":"基于本地HTTP REST API的轻量级Obsidian-MCP桥接方案，零配置启动，兼容所有标准MCP服务。","descriptionEn":"MCP服务器通过Local REST API社区插件与Obsidian进行交互。","category":"network","tags":["REST API","零配置","标准协议","本地通信","协议兼容"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"@MarkusPfundstein-mcp-obsidian","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"pypi","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/MarkusPfundstein/mcp-obsidian","source":"modelscope","configHint":"需Obsidian启用'Local REST API'插件（v1.2+），默认监听localhost:3000","envSchema":{"OBSIDIAN_API_KEY":{"description":"Your API key for the Obsidian REST API. This key can be found in the Obsidian plugin config.","type":"string"}},"envRequired":["OBSIDIAN_API_KEY"],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["快速集成","协议调试","MCP服务测试","低代码连接"]},{"serverId":"wcs37a-StarWhisper-observation-calculator","friendlyName":"星语观星计算器","friendlyNameEn":"StarWhisper 天文可观测性计算器","description":"基于天文学库的本地化可观测性分析工具，支持自定义经纬度、目标天体与观测约束条件，生成高度曲线与窗口时段。","descriptionEn":"\n## For modelscope托管\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"StarWhisper-observation\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"mcp_observability_server.py\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"PYTHONPATH\": \".\"\n      },\n      \"description\": \"StarWhisper天文可观测性计算器MCP服务器\",\n      \"version\": \"1.0.0\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"calculate_observability\": {\n      \"name\": \"calculate_observability\",\n      \"description\": \"计算指定天文目标的可观测性\",\n      \"inputSchema\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"latitude\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"观测站纬度（度）\",\n            \"minimum\": 0,\n            \"maximum\": 90\n          },\n          \"longitude\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"观测站经度（度）\",\n            \"minimum\": -180,\n            \"maximum\": 180\n          },\n          \"target_name\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"目标名称（如'Vega', 'moon', 'mars'等）\"\n          },\n          \"altitude\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"观测站海拔（米）\",\n            \"default\": 0.0\n          },\n          \"min_altitude\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"最小地平高度（度）\",\n            \"default\": 30.0,\n            \"minimum\": 0,\n            \"maximum\": 90\n          },\n          \"min_moon_separation\": {\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"description\": \"最小月距（度）\",\n            \"default\": 30.0,\n            \"minimum\": 0,\n            \"maximum\": 180\n          },\n          \"time_range_hours\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"检查时间范围（小时）\",\n            \"default\": 24,\n            \"minimum\": 1,\n            \"maximum\": 168\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\"latitude\", \"longitude\", \"target_name\"]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"examples\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"查询Vega可观测性\",\n      \"description\": \"在新昌观测站查询Vega的可观测性\",\n      \"input\": {\n        \"latitude\": 29.501784,\n        \"longitude\": 120.905740,\n        \"target_name\": \"Vega\",\n        \"min_altitude\": 30.0,\n        \"min_moon_separation\": 30.0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"查询月球可观测性\",\n      \"description\": \"在新昌观测站查询月球的可观测性\",\n      \"input\": {\n        \"latitude\": 29.501784,\n        \"longitude\": 120.905740,\n        \"target_name\": \"moon\",\n        \"min_altitude\": 20.0,\n        \"min_moon_separation\": 0.0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"查询火星可观测性\",\n      \"description\": \"在新昌观测站查询火星的可观测性\",\n      \"input\": {\n        \"latitude\": 29.501784,\n        \"longitude\": 120.905740,\n        \"target_name\": \"M31\",\n        \"min_altitude\": 30.0,\n        \"min_moon_separation\": 30.0\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"name\": \"StarWhisper-observation-calculator\",\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"description\": \"计算天文目标的可观测性，包括高度曲线和约束条件检查\",\n    \"author\": \"Cunshi Wang\",\n    \"license\": \"MIT\",\n    \"repository\": \"https://github.com/example/StarWhisper-observation-calculator\",\n    \"keywords\": [\n      \"astronomy\",\n      \"observability\",\n      \"mcp\",\n      \"astropy\",\n      \"simbad\"\n    ],\n    \"dependencies\": [\n      \"astropy>=5.0.0\",\n      \"astroquery>=0.4.6\",\n      \"astroplan>=0.8.0\",\n      \"numpy>=1.20.0\"\n    ],\n    \"python_version\": \">=3.8\"\n  }\n}","category":"development","tags":["天文计算","观测规划","AstroPy","Python","科研工具","本地运行","星图分析","教育科研"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"wcs37a-StarWhisper-observation-calculator","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/wcs37/StarWhisper-observation-calculator","source":"modelscope","configHint":"需安装 astropy/astroquery/astroplan 等天文计算依赖，推荐使用 conda 环境管理","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["天文观测规划","科普教学","业余天文台调度","科研辅助"]},{"serverId":"shuawking-mcp-obsidian","friendlyName":"Obsidian 智能文件中枢","friendlyNameEn":"mcp-obsidian","description":"为 Obsidian 笔记库提供标准化 MCP 接口，支持文件读写、全文检索与结构化编辑，实现 LLM 与本地知识库无缝协同。","descriptionEn":"该项目提供了一个通过本地 REST API 社区插件与 Obsidian 交互的 MCP 服务器。它包括列出文件、获取文件内容、搜索、修补、追加和删除 Obsidian 仓库中内容的工具。","category":"filesystem","tags":["笔记管理","本地知识库","Obsidian","文件操作","MCP协议","LLM集成","私有数据","Zettelkasten"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"shuawking-mcp-obsidian","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/MarkusPfundstein/mcp-obsidian","source":"modelscope","configHint":"需配合 Obsidian 社区插件 'MCP Server' 使用；Windows 需启用 WSL 或 PowerShell 权限策略","envSchema":{"OBSIDIAN_API_KEY":{"description":"<YOUR_OBSIDIAN_API_KEY>","type":"string"},"OBSIDIAN_HOST":{"description":"<your_obsidian_host>","type":"string"},"OBSIDIAN_PORT":{"description":"<your_obsidian_port>","type":"string"}},"envRequired":["OBSIDIAN_API_KEY","OBSIDIAN_HOST","OBSIDIAN_PORT"],